des:
Diamondbacks fan trivia was amassed by a long time avid fan of Major League Baseball. This skill is fun to play during the long winter months when there is no baseball and you long to hear “Play Ball”. Or before or after the game while at home or in the car.

Diamondbacks Fan trivia is great for the entire family. Play by yourself or against others to see who really knows their D-Backs.

New trivia is constantly being added to the skill so keep coming back and playing.

If you have questions, comments or a favorite trivia you want to see added to this game please let us know: skills@dwilsys.com.
